    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It seems to work now, indeed.\r\n\r\nThe thing is that these are generated with [Doctoc](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/package.json#L22), which will override your changes every time the command is run again.\r\n\r\nThe easy solution that I see right now would be to either find emojis that work in links, or remove all emojis in headers.",
